data.description:
BYOB- Bring your own builder! This 1.44 acre lot is ready to build on in Royse City. Your land is located in the new residential community of Vista Oaks Estates. City services and wide concrete roads, but keeping that country home feel. Build a 2400 square foot or larger house within the community guidelines. 
Adjacent to FM 1565 within the city limits. One mile from I-30. Minutes from Royse City shopping, restaurants, golf, and more. 40 minutes east of downtown Dallas.
